turns.content:
Based on our Standard Model of Code with 16 SCALE levels (Bit → Universe) and the physics analogy of RG flow (UV internal → IR external), create an ASCII diagram showing:

1. The 16 SCALE levels arranged on an IN/OUT axis (not vertical hierarchy)
2. Where INTERNAL knowledge (Collider/Gemini) applies vs EXTERNAL knowledge (Perplexity/Web)
3. The BOUNDARY zone where code meets world
4. How the centripetal scan moves from EXTERNAL → INTERNAL

Use the convention: vertical = scale energy, horizontal = internal/external separation.

Make the diagram suitable for inclusion in documentation.
